comments: Nesmith (IND) briefly extends both hands to Randle (NYK) and marginal contact occurs as he defends the pick.
Nesmith (IND) is absorbing the initial contact that occurs with Grimes (NYK) and incidental contact occurs as Grimes (NYK) attempts to move over the pick.
Randle (NYK) and Nesmith (IND) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Grimes (NYK) maintains his arms within the frame of his body and does not deliver illegal contact to Nesmith (IND) during the screen.
Nembhard (IND) grabs and pulls Randle's (NYK) arm that affects his FOM off-ball. Replay review of the foul called on Nembhard (NYK) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Nesmith (IND) firms up in Grimes' (NYK) path and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Barrett (NYK) is moving alongside Hield's (IND) path and marginal body contact occurs during Hield's (IND) drive.
Randle (NYK) initiates marginal contact with Haliburton (IND) off-ball.
Nembhard (IND) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Grimes (NYK) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Randle (NYK) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds. Possession is correctly awarded to the Pacers.
After the ball becomes loose, Nembhard (IND) and Randle (NYK) mutually engage and disengage.
After making contact with the ball Nesmith (IND) makes incidental contact with Randle's (NYK) arm.
Mathurin (IND) dislodges the ball out of bounds. NYK is correctly awarded the possession.
Hield (IND) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Barrett (NYK) commits a take foul on Haliburton (IND).
Haliburton (IND) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
